text: Jung Jin-hee (born 10 April 1985) is a South Korean taekwondo practitioner. She won a gold medal in bantamweight at the 2007 World Taekwondo Championships in Beijing. She won a bronze medal at the 2010 Asian Taekwondo Championships. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists Category:Asian Taekwondo Championships medalists
